videos.description: QB Nathan Rourke connects with Isiah Cox, who makes a man miss and dashes all the way to the 5-yard line, setting up A.J. Ouellette's 2-yard touchdown run to make it 7-3 Bobcats.
videos.headline: Ohio uses 70-yard catch-and-run to set up TD

videos.description: WR D.J. Brown takes the jet sweep and shoots through a hole, getting to the end zone and making it 9-7 Huskies.
videos.headline: Northern Illinois responds with 28-yard TD run

videos.description: DB Trayshon Foster cuts in front of a Nathan Rourke pass, making the interception and returning it into Ohio territory.
videos.headline: Northern Illinois comes up with big INT

videos.description: QB Nathan Rourke avoids the rush and finds a wide-open Isiah Cox, who scores his 2nd touchdown of the game and gives the Bobcats a 14-9 lead.
videos.headline: Ohio reclaims lead on 56-yard TD pass

videos.description: QB Nathan Rourke throws on target to an unguarded Connor Brown, who walks into the end zone and makes it 21-9 Bobcats.
videos.headline: Ohio extends lead with 11-yard TD pass

videos.description: DE Sutton Smith gets to Nathan Rourke and jars the ball free before falling on it to give the Huskies possession late in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Northern Illinois creates huge strip sack

videos.description: RB Marcus Jones finds paydirt on a 2-yard touchdown run, and the Huskies execute the two-point conversion with a trick-play throw to OL Max Scharping.
videos.headline: Northern Illinois takes lead on TD and 2-point conversion
